{"tid":1943053,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解疫境特別多黃店受攻擊？","createTime":"2020-03-25T12:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T15:18:06.000Z","uid":160257,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2444f38c1e3811e35f5c7e83473e270c5415c298","tid":1943053,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:00:54.000Z","msg":"因為疫境好多鋪頭都勁難捱，不論黃藍錄都未必捱得住，哩個時候<span style=\"color: red;\">正正係壯大黃色經濟圈嘅最好機會</span>，對家當然都明白哩個道理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋只需要堅持只喺自己信任嘅黃店入面消費（自己要判斷佢真黃偽黃，好食唔好食，繼唔繼續幫襯）幫佢哋捱過疫情。<br />\n<br />\n而捱唔過嘅藍店就可以say byebye <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最理想嘅情況係有更多鋪頭轉黃（不論真偽）</span>，等黃圈壯大，等黃絲有更多選擇，等藍屍只有黃店揀，等黃圈入面有競爭，繼而提升質素。<br />\n<br />\n但不斷提高門檻變相批鬥黃店，只會令黃店承受嘅成本變高，又要應付黃絲，又要驚藍屍攻擊，叫人點轉軚？黃圈點壯大？<br />\n<br />\n一句到尾，<span style=\"color: red;\">只要你打算消費，咁就幫襯自己信任嘅黃店！</span>根本零風險，人人都要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afa9e8df8d14ebc4a552e659eba72b8ef0ebdd5","tid":1943053,"uid":160257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"事實上情況係，市面上可以選擇嘅黃店唔夠多，好多黃絲被迫幫襯綠店，係咪應該扭轉哩個情況呢？"},{"pid":"42067b80f3e8905149d258a3b177fa2fbd78f128","tid":1943053,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7012f10c5752e0d8807d1d63864772e5e9b58014","tid":1943053,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:06:28.000Z","msg":"同場加演<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過用黃色經濟圈分化返對家？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1941625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1941625</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cfe268f5ebd1975ab30578e07974925e3236e902","tid":1943053,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"值得一睇<br />\n<br />\n其實大家搞清楚咩叫黃色經濟圈未<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1942642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1942642</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c993d0c06b3ea51b1655b6ccf89c2673c881a54","tid":1943053,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:08:18.000Z","msg":"日日食黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed92de9ea98758916cf25bc729b81e626336594","tid":1943053,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c993d0c06b3ea51b1655b6ccf89c2673c881a54","tid":1943053,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:08:18.000Z","msg":"日日食黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"不過都要注意衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912d86eb7460720a9838fdbd433d3b0ecd1eaeac","tid":1943053,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"同一諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建立「黃色經濟圈」最好嘅方法，唔只幫趁黃店！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1943000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1943000</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9f8b2150457903313b905298ea35ca1ba9a5adde","tid":1943053,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:12:02.000Z","msg":"支持原因就係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疫情愈嚴重，愈要堅持「黃色經濟圈」，掌握經濟下行「救生艇」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848553</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13644fc00d9e06af7d950417a7d78a6bac86ff63","tid":194305